195
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:55,360
<font color="#8080FF">ŁOSKOT</font>

196
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:02,520
<font color="#8080FF">WZDYCHA CIĘŻKO</font>

197
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:20,000
